title: A Conversation with Queen Latifah
description: Neil deGrasse Tyson has an in-depth, one-on-one conversation with recording artist and actress Queen Latifah about the role science has played in her life, being a Trekkie, hip hop, Ice Age 5, and the science fiction martial arts film she wants to make.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
